data.description: Motivated Seller!! Furniture is negotiable. Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home located in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Laurel Estates. Step inside and be greeted by the beautiful epoxy floors that gracefully lead you into a spacious and open formal living room and dining room area. The heart of the home boasts a large gourmet kitchen that seamlessly flows into the family room, perfect for hosting gatherings and creating cherished memories. The kitchen features a newly installed backsplash, adding a touch of elegance to the space.  Convenience is key with a guest bedroom and full bathroom situated downstairs, providing a private retreat for visitors. As you make your way upstairs, you'll be delighted to find a generous loft area, offering endless possibilities such as a gaming zone, home theater, or any other creative endeavor. The main bedroom is a true oasis, impressively spacious with its own sitting area. Enjoy the luxury of an ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet, making it a perfect sanctuary to unwind after a long day. The second floor also encompasses three generously sized bedrooms that can be flexibly used as guest rooms, offices, an in-home gym, or even a craft room – tailored to suit your lifestyle. To add to the modern comforts, the home is equipped with upgraded recess lighting, Alexa devices in every room, and a digital thermostat. Embrace the convenience of controlling light dimmers through your phone and enjoy the ease of keyless entry installed on the front door, along with additional security provided by strategically placed cameras around the property. Enhancing the charm and character of the home, pine baseboards have been meticulously installed on the first floor, complementing the elegance of the hardwood stairs. Lastly, a practical garage storage solution has been thoughtfully implemented to keep your space organized and clutter-free. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a beautiful home with abundant features in the desirable Laurel Estates neighborhood. Come and make this property your dream haven today!
